PN,38401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FThe Government must appoint a national
OL,8,Fmaternity commissioner with the legal
OL,9,Fpowers to drive change in order to
OL,10,Freduce harm to families from repeated
OL,11,Ffailures in NHS care, a report has
OL,12,Fconcluded.
OL,14,FThe new "rapid review" into maternity
OL,15,Fcare, led by Baroness Valerie Amos,
OL,16,Fcalls for urgent change to the way
OL,17,Fwomen and families are treated,
OL,18,Fincluding when they phone in with
OL,19,Fconcerns during pregnancy and labour.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FAmong the 12 NHS Trusts included in
OL,8,Fthe report are: University Hospitals
OL,9,FSussex NHS Foundation Trust, Oxford
OL,10,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Foundation
OL,11,FTrust and East Kent Hospitals NHS
OL,12,FFoundation Trust.
OL,14,FThe Amos review gathered the views of
OL,15,Fmore than 450 families and received
OL,16,Fover 10,500 responses to a public call
OL,17,Ffor evidence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FThe report highlights key areas of
OL,8,Fconcern, identifies barriers to
OL,9,Fdelivering change and sets out a
OL,10,Frobust package of recommendations
OL,11,Faimed at delivering long-term systemic
OL,12,Fand cultural transformation in
OL,13,Fmaternity and neonatal care for the
OL,14,F21st century, with accountability,
OL,15,Fequity, excellence and compassion at
OL,16,Fits core.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FLady Amos said families should have
OL,8,Fthe right to an independent
OL,9,Finvestigation of their care when
OL,10,Fthings go wrong and that they do not
OL,11,Fagree with the findings of internal
OL,12,FNHS reviews.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FShe pointed to the need to improve the
OL,8,Fculture in hospitals and teamworking
OL,9,Fbetween midwives, obstetricians and
OL,10,Fother medics, and suggested an
OL,11,Foverhaul of rotas to ensure obstetric
OL,12,Fconsultants and anaesthetists are
OL,13,Favailable on a delivery unit "for
OL,14,Ftimely critical senior decision making
OL,15,Fand intervention 24 hours a day, seven
OL,16,Fdays a week".
OL,26,@uD@^OUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FWhile "the vast majority of
OL,8,Fpregnancies and births in England have
OL,9,Fa positive outcome and we have seen
OL,10,Fmany examples of good practice", Lady
OL,11,FAmos pointed to poor care embedded
OL,12,Facross the system.
OL,26,@oD@GOUrD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FNational leaders and other senior
OL,8,Fpeople described to assessors a
OL,9,Fmaternity and neonatal system in which
OL,10,Fthere is "fragmented governance, with
OL,11,Ftoo many organisations, an abundance
OL,12,Fof overlapping recommendations to be
OL,13,Fimplemented, an overwhelming amount of
OL,14,Fguidance, unclear lines of
OL,15,Fresponsibility and inadequate
OL,16,Fregulatory oversight for ensuring
OL,17,Fsafety and change".
OL,26,@rD@JOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FThey also said there were "persistent
OL,8,Fworkforce pressures, with shortages,
OL,9,Fattrition, rota gaps" and high staff
OL,10,Fabsence rates.
OL,12,FThe report further found care was
OL,13,Fbeing given "in poorly maintained and,
OL,14,Fat times, unsafe clinical
OL,15,Fenvironments".
OL,17,FUniversity Hospitals Sussex NHS
OL,18,FFoundation Trust
OL,26,@oD@[OUqD@UO]uD@MOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FDr Andy Heeps, Chief Executive at
OL,8,FUniversity Hospitals Sussex, said: "We
OL,9,Fknow there are families whose care
OL,10,Fherefell below the standards they had
OL,11,Fevery right to expect. I am deeply
OL,12,Fsorry for that, and for the harm and
OL,13,Fdistress they have suffered as a
OL,14,Fresult.
OL,16,F"Baroness Amos' report is clear we
OL,17,Fmust do better: in listening to women
OL,18,Fand families, in how we communicate,
OL,19,Fand how we respond when things are
OL,20,Fdifficult or go wrong.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"We are committed to doing that.
OL,8,FTelephone triage is one area that has
OL,9,Fbeen transformed in response to some
OL,10,Fof the experiences Baroness Amos
OL,11,Fheard, helping improve our performance
OL,12,Fon national safety and quality
OL,13,Fstandards.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"To keep improving, we will adopt all
OL,8,Fforthcoming national taskforce
OL,9,Frecommendations, continue using our
OL,10,Fown data and feedback to raise
OL,11,Fstandards, and ensure the voices of
OL,12,Fthe families we serve guide our
OL,13,Fefforts to provide safer, kinder
OL,14,Fmaternity care."
OL,16,FOxford University Hospitals NHS
OL,17,FFoundation Trust
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FSimon Crowther, Interim Chief
OL,8,FExecutive Officer, Oxford University
OL,9,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust, said:
OL,10,F"We apologise unreservedly to the
OL,11,Fwomen, babies and families who
OL,12,Fsuffered in our care, or whose
OL,13,Fexperience caused them grief or
OL,14,Fdistress. We failed them at some of
OL,15,Fthe most important and vulnerable
OL,16,Fmoments of their lives. We accept what
OL,17,Ffamilies have told the investigation,
OL,18,Fthe failings in care they describe in
OL,19,Fthe report, and our responsibility to
OL,20,Fact...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"...We know that families' trust and
OL,8,Fconfidence in our maternity services
OL,9,Fhave been badly damaged. We also know
OL,10,Fthey will not be rebuilt by words
OL,11,Falone, and that what matters now is
OL,12,Fwhat we do next.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"We will place the experiences shared
OL,8,Fwith Baroness Amos and her team at the
OL,9,Fheart of our improvement plans. Women,
OL,10,Ffamilies and staff will be directly
OL,11,Finvolved in informing, shaping and
OL,12,Fdelivering the changes we make. We
OL,13,Fwill listen, act honestly, and be open
OL,14,Fabout the progress we are making and
OL,15,Fthe progress we still have to make.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"Our most recent CQC inspection
OL,8,Frecognised that change has begun, but
OL,9,Fthe experiences in this report show
OL,10,Fhow far we still have to travel, and
OL,11,Fwe do not underestimate that distance.
OL,12,FWe will listen harder, act faster, and
OL,13,Fhold ourselves accountable for the
OL,14,Fimprovements that women, babies,
OL,15,Ffamilies and staff have every right to
OL,16,Fexpect.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"We will respond to both the national
OL,8,Freport and our own local report in
OL,9,Ffull, and we will act on them with
OL,10,Furgency. We will say clearly what we
OL,11,Fare changing, by when, and how women
OL,12,Fand families will see the difference.
OL,13,FAnd we will keep saying it, openly and
OL,14,Fhonestly, until trust in our services
OL,15,Fis rebuilt.
OL,17,F"To every woman, baby and family we
OL,18,Ffailed, we are sorry. We have heard
OL,19,Fyou, and we are determined to be the
OL,20,Fservice you deserve."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G16/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FEast Kent Hospitals NHS Foundation
OL,8,FTrust
OL,10,FDr Des Holden, acting chief executive
OL,11,Ffor East Kent Hospitals, said: "We
OL,12,Frecognise and are truly sorry for the
OL,13,Fdevastating and ongoing impact for
OL,14,Ffamilies of failings in our service.
OL,15,FWe know that the experiences
OL,16,Fhighlighted in Baroness Amos' report
OL,17,Fare not acceptable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G17/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"Today's report identifies a number of
OL,8,Fpositive changes within our maternity
OL,9,Fservice since the publication of Dr
OL,10,FBill Kirkup's 'Reading the signals'
OL,11,Finvestigation in 2022. It also
OL,12,Fdescribes concerns raised by families
OL,13,Fand staff that we fully acknowledge
OL,14,Fand are responding to.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G18/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38419
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"We are committed to continuing our
OL,8,Fimprovement programme to ensure long-
OL,9,Fterm, consistent and sustained change
OL,10,Fin maternity and neonatal care, for
OL,11,Ffamilies and staff. We are grateful to
OL,12,Fstaff and service users who enabled
OL,13,Fthe CQC to rate our services as 'good'
OL,14,Fat both WHH and QEQM in 2025. We will
OL,15,Fensure the learning from today's
OL,16,Freport is addressed and taken forward,
OL,17,Fand we will openly report on our
OL,18,Fprogress through our Trust Board held
OL,19,Fin public."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G19/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38420
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FThe National Maternity and Neonatal
OL,8,FTaskforce, chaired by the Secretary of
OL,9,FState for Health and Social Care, will
OL,10,Fdevelop and oversee a new national
OL,11,Faction plan in response to Baroness
OL,12,FAmos's findings.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G20/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38421
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782827280
OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FBaroness Amos said: "Women, babies and
OL,8,Ffamilies deserve maternity and
OL,9,Fneonatal care that is safe,
OL,10,Fcompassionate and equitable wherever
OL,11,Fthey live. Too often, this
OL,12,FInvestigation heard that people were
OL,13,Fnot listened to, that harm was
OL,14,Frepeated, and that families were left
OL,15,Fwithout clear answers or
OL,16,Faccountability when things went wrong.
OL,26,@oD@UOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G21/22
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
