OL,3,CKent, Oxford and Sussex maternity
OL,4,Cunits in need of 'urgent reform' after
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"This report sets out practical action
OL,8,Fto change that. It recommends stronger
OL,9,Fnational leadership, clearer
OL,10,Faccountability, better listening,
OL,11,Fsafer service design, improved
OL,12,Finvestigations, stronger team working
OL,13,Fand leadership, and investment in the
OL,14,Fbuildings and digital systems where
OL,15,Ffamilies receive care and deliver it.
OL,17,F"These recommendations must be
OL,18,Fimplemented in full. They are designed
OL,19,Fto deliver lasting system change,
OL,20,Fstrengthen accountability, and create
OL,21,Fa system that learns when harm occurs."
